content: e-v news facebook carve out internet empires master english e-v news facebook carve out internet empires date march 30 2017 a_uthor masterenglish247 comments google facebook carve out internet empires google facebook ngốn thị_trường internet toàn_cầu as the above map shows google dominates much of the_west and_india while facebook can claim supremacy in the middle east north_africa and much of_the spanish-speaking americas bản_đồ google cai_trị khu_vực tây ấn_độ facebook chiếm_lĩnh trung_đông bắc phi khu_vực châu_mỹ tiếng tây ban_nha while facebook has carved out large chunk of_the global internet market researchers point out that in the countries where the social media site was most popular google is not far behind facebook ngốn miếng bánh thị_trường internet toàn_cầu nhà_nghiên_cứu quốc_gia mạng xã_hội rầm_rộ google bám sát nút among the 50 countries that have facebook listed as the most visited website 36 of_them have google as the second most visited and_the remaining 14 countries list youtube currently owned by google according to the_research nghiên_cứu 50 quốc_gia facebook dẫn_đầu trang_web truy_cập 36 google xếp hai 14 youtube hiện sở_hữu google asia meanwhile is more of a_patchwork with baidu search engine dominating that half billion internet users researchers also found that baidu was the top site in south korea but admit that could be result_of skewed data on the other hand they say it could reflect ambitions beyond china mền chắp_vá mảnh châu_á thống_trị công_cụ tìm_kiếm baidu trung_quốc nửa tỉ internet quốc_gia nhà_nghiên_cứu baidu truy_cập nam triều_tiên dữ_liệu sai_lệch mặt_khác phản_ánh tham_vọng thống_trị baidu lãnh_thổ trung_quốc japan and_taiwan are outliers in asia because yahoo is the most popular site in those countries nhật_bản đài_loan kẻ ngoại_lai yahoo trang_web thông_dụng quốc_gia while data was not available for sub-saharan africa most countries that have significant internet population are covered kenya madagascar nigeria and_south africa fall within the sphere of empire whereas ghana senegal and_sudan have been subsumed within dominion according to the_research nhà_nghiên_cứu dữ_liệu khu_vực châu_phi nam sahara đông internet chiếm_lĩnh kenya madagascar nigeria nam phi_chịu thống_trị google ghana senegal sudan thuộc_địa facebook we are likely still in the very beginning of_the age of internet empires but it may well be that the territories carved out now will have important implications for which companies end up controlling how we_communicate and_access information for many years to_come the researchers concluded nhà_nghiên_cứu kết_luận ngấp_nghé ngưỡng_cửa thời_đại đế_chế internet phân_vùng sức ảnh_hưởng công_ty kiểm_soát cách_thức truyền_đạt truy_cập thông_tin the data used in the research was collected by the company alexa which has provided web analytics since 1996 dữ_liệu nghiên_cứu công_ty alexa thu_thập công_ty chuyên cung_cấp dữ_liệu phân_tích internet 1996
